   &UR; ROBOTIC SURGERY &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; ONE COLOR SLIDE IS AVAILABLE FREE &QL; 
 &UR; (700 words) &QL; 
 &UR; By KATHY A. SVITIL &LR;  &QC;
