<P>
   SUMMER-SALAD _ Frying, searing and melting? Then you're
experiencing the South Florida summer with the rest of us. So who
cooks when it's this hot?
</P>
<P>
   Still, you have to eat. What you need is something cold and
savory _ and here's the key _ prepared by someone else. (Norris,
Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
