</P>
<P>
   SALAD-SIDE _ Takeout is our first choice for quick, cool summer
meals, but if you're going to make your own, keep it simple. The
most you should do is boil pasta, as for the first recipe by Marcel
Desaulniers. The recipe is featured in his new book, ``Salad Days''
(Simon &AMP; Schuster, $27.50.) Note that the recipes in the book,
while inspired, are lengthy and involve several steps. (Recipes
follow.) Sidebar to SUMMER-SALAD. (Norris, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
