RYAN-MOVIE (Los Angeles) _ Tom Hanks doesn't look like an action
hero. He has never acted the part in a film, either. So the fact
that he's playing the platoon captain in Steven Spielberg's brutal
new war film, ``Saving Private Ryan,'' offers a telling clue about
