storytelling instincts at his formidable command, Steven Spielberg
hasn't just made a picture that looks as artfully awful as war can
be. He's made an unflinching _ and because of that, truly
respectful _ examination of what it can do to men's behavior as
well as their bodies. 2 Stars. By Bob Strauss. 
