<HEADER>
A0125 &Cx1f; tab-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CYBERTIMES-BUDGET-NYT     07-23 0298
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CYBERTIMES-BUDGET-NYTSF </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The following articles constitute this week's transmission of
The New York Times Syndicate's CyberTimes package. All have been
sent to category codes ``l'' lifestyle news and ``f'' business
news.
</P>
<P>
   1. ``TRAVEL LOG: FENDER-BENDERS ON THE DIGITAL HIGHWAY''
</P>
<P>
   A colleague claims she suffers from BLK _ Bad 'Lectronic Karma.
She believes that her mere presence causes electronic devices to
malfunction. BLK quickly ensued when testing two new multifunction
cards for the PC.
</P>
<P>
   SLUGGED: BC-CYBERTIMES-TRAVEL-COLUMN-NYTSF
