   _ 3Com Megahertz cards: http://www.3com.com/client/mcd/products/
</P>
<P>
   _ What's a dongle? (1993 definition):
http://huis.huis.hiroshima-u.ac.jp/Computer/Jargon/LexiconEntries/D
ongle.html
</P>
<P>
   _ Rainbow Technologies' ``Don Gall'' ad:
http://www.rnbo.com/products/DONGALL.HTM
</P>
