   (NYT19) NEW YORK -- July 23, 1998 -- NY-PORN-SHOPS, 7-23 -- In
an attempt to conform with new sex shop laws, workers from the Big
Top Lounge on 8th Avenue carry out the remnants of demolished
``exotic dancer'' booths. Giving a glimmer of hope to the owners of
