   (NYT2) NEW YORK -- July 23, 1998 -- ADV. FOR SUN., JULY 26 --
EAGLEN/SCHAFER-ALBUMS, 7-22 -- Christine Schafer performing with
members of the Metropolitan Opera Orchestra at the Pierpont Morgan
Library in Manhattan earlier this year. Ms. Schafer's most album
(Deutsche Grammophon 289 457 582-2) has a unique mix of arias from
Mozart and love songs and lullabies from Strauss. (G. Paul
Burnett/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT1) NEW YORK -- July 23, 1998 -- ADV. FOR SUN., JULY 26 --
CANBY-THEATER, 7-22 -- Max Wright, left, as Sir Andrew Aguecheek
and Brian Murray as Sir Toby Belch in Shakespeares's ``Twelfth
Night'' at the Vivian Beaumont Theater at Lincoln Center. The play,
directed by Nicholas Hytner, is scheduled to run through Aug. 30,
as part of the Lincoln Center Festival '98.(Sara Krulwich/New York
Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
