<DOCNO> NYT19980723.0525 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-23 23:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0519 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CADET-TRIAL-1STLD-WRI     07-23 0940
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CADET-TRIAL-1STLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
JURORS TO DECIDE FATE OF FORMER AIR FORCE CADET 

</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  (Sub for minor editing throughout) 
(Eds.: No verdict as of 9:30 p.m., CDT) 
 
